{"tid":1190974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好似俾人呃錢","createTime":"2019-06-07T16:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T16:27:33.000Z","uid":158325,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca961d45d30eb19193fe65660397cd6c10702360","tid":1190974,"uid":158325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:00:44.000Z","msg":"頭先喺朗記落緊電梯<br />\n突然前面有嗰㗎仔問彌敦道點去<br />\n睇完佢地圖原來想搭E21趕去機場<br />\n我見自己又得閒咪諗住幫佢<br />\n途中同佢用英文吹水,有少少日本口音但講得幾標準<br />\n佢話自己喺27歲大學生,自己1個嚟香港玩,好鍾意香港<br />\n又話自己有用wts,佢比咗佢電話我叫我得閒wts佢<br />\n一路都行到好快,我諗佢應該都好趕時間<br />\n去到巴士站,佢就問要搭幾耐車,話自己好趕時間,11:40分就飛但果時都10:20分<br />\n咁我就帶佢去搭的士,但佢話佢得150港紙喺身唔係好夠<br />\n後尾帶到佢上的士,之後諗住借2舊水俾佢搭點都夠,點知佢話唔夠借多少少比佢,我心諗日本人應該冇問題嘅又有佢wts,點知佢上車之後諗住wts佢,個電話入極都唔啱wts唔到,我點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2dd9eeb857eecd7c924c0e981ae22135f06c801","tid":1190974,"uid":52299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:02:44.000Z","msg":"on9 日本仔撚知去機場幾錢咩"},{"pid":"5b4587eb8df108ad8a5f1d71c5254aea935a9dae","tid":1190974,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:04:16.000Z","msg":"你已經俾人呃左"},{"pid":"122f637fb21f0857c0c08b6276e2a814f5647467","tid":1190974,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:04:49.000Z","msg":"[大家小心]日本人自稱趕飛機借錢搭的士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/992968/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/992968/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"344bd3154db4bf0afe37a3376de02c5c6f37a1e9","tid":1190974,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T16:05:21.000Z","msg":"秒經"},{"pid":"cde6b575878c9022880214eeb76387328c5e09